Package: dsmSearch
Type: Package
Title: DSM and LiDAR Downloader
Version: 1.2.2
Authors@R: c(person("Xiaohao", "Yang", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"),
        email = "xiaohaoy@umich.edu"), person("Nathan", "Fox", role =
        c("aut")), person("Derek", "Van Berkel", role = c("aut")),
        person("Mark", "Lindquist", role = c("aut")))
Description: A collection of functions to search and download Digital
        Surface Model (DSM) and Light Detection and Ranging (LiDAR)
        data via APIs, including 'OpenTopography'
        <https://portal.opentopography.org/apidocs/> and 'TNMAccess'
        <https://apps.nationalmap.gov/tnmaccess/#/>, and canopy tree
        height data.
